#

Classic Beef Wellington with Creamy Mashed Potatoes and Buttered Green Beans

$45
800 kcal
Difficulty: 70%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

glutendairyegg

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinglutendairy

Tags:

gourmetelegantholidaycomfort food

Description

A luxurious Beef Wellington wrapped in flaky pastry, served with rich mashed potatoes and fresh green beans.

Ingredients

  • beef tenderloin: 1 lb
  • puff pastry: 1 sheet
  • mushrooms: 8 oz
  • prosciutto: 4 slices
  • Dijon mustard: 2 tbsp
  • egg: 1, beaten
  • potatoes: 2 lbs
  • butter: 4 tbsp
  • heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • green beans: 1 lb
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
